Title: Day 5: 8:00 P.M. - 9:00 P.M.
Plot:
Jack bargains with a German intelligence agent in order to find the woman who can lead him to Bierko. 

Buchanan chafes against the new chain of command as Homeland Security prepares to take over CTU operations. 

Aaron receives a request for a secret meeting from Wayne Palmer, as Logan implements martial law in L.A.
